thread.title: BRIEF-Sichuan Kelun Pharmaceutical sees FY 2017 net profit to up 15 pct to 45 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Sichuan Kelun Pharmaceutical sees FY 2017 net profit to up 15 pct to 45 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - sichuan kelun pharmaceutical co ltd

text:
Jan 31 (Reuters) - Sichuan Kelun Pharmaceutical Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 15 percent to 45 percent, or to be 672.3 million yuan to 847.7 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 584.6 million yuan
* Says increase in investment revenue as main reason for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/HRgYaz
